history.content: UPE and Mayfield are bringing you another hiring fair with some of Mayfield Fund's exciting portfolio companies! Please join us for an evening where we’ll spend a few minutes providing a high-level look at the current venture capital market and startup ecosystem, then transition into hearing from a few of our portfolio companies on their entry level and other hiring needs. When: March 14, 2022, 5-7PM Where: Sibley Auditorium RSVP/More Info: https://events.mayfield.com/upe-hiring-fair-with-mayfield-fund-portfolio-companies Additionally, all participants will have the opportunity to receive a long sleeve Mayfield X UPE t-shirt as part of our exit survey during the event. To wrap things up, we'll break out for an unstructured networking and Ike's sandwich reception where participating students will have the opportunity to meet and chat with Applied Cognition, Balbix, Couchbase, DevRev, Highbeam and others.
history.subject: UPExMayfield Hiring Fair on 3/14
